            <title>[CASSANDRA-3651] Truncate shouldn&apos;t rethrow timeouts as UA</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-3651</link>
                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Truncate is a very easy operation to timeout, but the timeouts rethrow as UnavailableException which is somewhat confusing.  Instead it should throw TimedOutException.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
